This Is My first Deathrun map.</br>


Map features:</br>
- 4 Nades (3 Are Secret)</br>
- 3 Minigames that are:</br>
 1. Easy</br>
 2. Bhop</br>
 3. Knife</br>
- 12 Traps (2 aren't activated by the terrorists)</br>
- 3 Minecraft Background Music</br>
</br>
Special Thanks to UNREAL For help me out on the map</br>
and thanks to the testers of the map.</br>
</br>
Hope You like the map, if you find any bug please tell me.
